    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having always been garage-kept and serviced exclusively at the dealership. This is a rare find for a collector or anyone seeking a car that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
