      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. The S54 inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, with the dual-VANOS system recently overhauled and rod bearings replaced as preventative measures. The subframe has been reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates to ensure structural rigidity. This example features a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Finished in concours-quality paint with a flawless undercarriage, this vehicle represents a turnkey investment for the discerning collector seeking peak mechanical harmony.",
